Provider API Endpoint Classes

provider.Rd

Provider API Endpoint Classes

Usage

pro_endpoint(alias)

pro_group(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <pro_endpoint> or<pro_group> object
